bio.openEndedText: I'm very passionate about cars, I have enjoyed reading about them ever since I was a kid. Ever since I started renting cars I have enjoyed meeting new people, customer service and quality cars are very important to me. I strive to accommodate my customers to the best of my ability. I'm also willing to deliver cars to customers, all you have to do is type in the address of where you want me to bring the vehicle or you can choose from the list that's on my car page. Every car is delivered clean and on time. ANOTHER PLUS ABOUT THE MAJORITY OF MY VEHICLES THAT WILL BENEFIT YOU AS A RENTER, THEY ARE VERY FUEL ⛽️ EFFICIENT.
